msgid ""
"<1.so>A Hylian?<2.pa> That's a rare sight so far\n"
"from your homeland.<3.ra>My orders from the <4.se_co>chief<5.re_co> are "
"to\n"
"monitor the <6.se_co>Divine Beast<7.re_co> from here.<8.ra>The "
"<9.se_co>sandstorms and lightning are fierce<10.re_co>\n"
"around that thing.<11.pa> You're as mortal as\n"
"anyone, so don't get too close."
